#happybirthday 🎈 Hands down my mother  @erikap0316 aka @anursespointofview is one of the most resilient women I know. It’s been 4+ yrs of her being diagnosed with Stage IV Lung cancer & a slew of other diagnoses thrown her way, and yet she hasn’t wavered. Her reason why she is fighting is so strong , it’s what’s keeping her going everyday. She’s the kind of woman who manages to bake pies, or make handmade Mala Beads, Fill a bedroom hole with drywall, or walk her Giant schnauzer JoJo or on the sewing machine finishing another purse she’s made. All of these sometimes right after a chemotherapy session. Eventually that burst of energy leaves & rest is needed for her body to reset. And then somehow she bounces back into her crafts & her canny sense of humor. Nurturing in ways only a Mother / Grandmother can give. How she manages to do this every day is commendable. To see you make 65 is a blessing in itself. I love you so much! Happy Birthday #Mom #loveyou #celebration 
❤️🥰📿🎂 ♓️
